{"type":"message","id":"06d88b89","parentId":"05044fe5","timestamp":"2026-03-16T07:14:40.699Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户发送了心跳消息，我需要：\n1. 读取 HEARTBEAT.md 文件\n2. 按照文件内容执行检查\n3. 如果没有需要关注的事情，回复 HEARTBEAT_OK\n\n让我先读取 HEARTBEAT.md 文件。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019cf57f3448593b97031673f9b82c68","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":8761,"output":135,"cacheRead":29440,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38336,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773645277697}}
{"type":"message","id":"6a8bd209","parentId":"06d88b89","timestamp":"2026-03-16T07:14:40.727Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019cf57f3448593b97031673f9b82c68","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# HEARTBEAT.md\n\n# 定期检查任务\n# AI 会在收到心跳消息时检查以下内容\n\n## 快速自检命令\n\n```bash\n# 完整健康检查\n/workspace/projects/workspace/scripts/health-check.sh\n\n# 带自动修复\n/workspace/projects/workspace/scripts/health-check.sh --fix\n```\n\n## 检查清单（按优先级轮换）\n\n### 高优先级（每次检查）\n- [ ] Gateway 进程是否运行\n- [ ] 端口 5000 是否响应\n- [ ] Hook 是否全部加载成功\n- [ ] 浏览器锁文件是否残留（SingletonLock 等）\n\n### 中优先级（每天检查一次）\n- [ ] 共享库是否正常加载\n- [ ] Skills 完整性（SKILL.md 是否存在）\n- [ ] 日志文件是否过大（超过 10MB）\n\n### 低优先级（每周检查一次）\n- [ ] 知识库是否需要更新\n- [ ] 代码规范是否需要调整\n- [ ] 回收站是否需要清理\n\n---\n\n## 心跳响应规则\n\n1. **检查时间**：只在 08:00 - 23:00 之间主动操作\n2. **静默时段**：23:00 - 08:00 只回复 HEARTBEAT_OK\n3. **批量处理**：多个检查合并为一次报告\n4. **避免打扰**：无问题时不发消息，只回复 HEARTBEAT_OK\n\n---\n\n## 自动修复项\n\n当运行 `--fix` 参数时，自动处理：\n- 清理残留锁文件\n- 清理超大日志文件（>10MB）\n- 清理无头浏览器僵尸进程\n\n---\n\n## 状态记录\n\n记录在 `storage/hooks/heartbeat-state.json`:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"lastCheck\": \"2026-03-16T12:00:00Z\",\n  \"lastClean\": \"2026-03-15T12:00:00Z\",\n  \"issues\": []\n}\n```\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773645280720}}
{"type":"message","id":"46117071","parentId":"6a8bd209","timestamp":"2026-03-16T07:14:46.570Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我已经读取了 HEARTBEAT.md 文件。现在我需要按照文件内容进行检查。\n\n根据心跳响应规则：\n1. 检查时间：当前是 3:14 PM (15:14)，在 08:00 - 23:00 之间，所以应该进行检查\n2. 需要执行高优先级的检查\n\n根据高优先级清单（每次检查）：\n- [ ] Gateway 进程是否运行\n- [ ] 端口 5000 是否响应\n- [ ] Hook 是否全部加载成功\n- [ ] 浏览器锁文件是否残留（SingletonLock 等）\n\n我应该先读取心跳状态文件，了解上次检查时间，然后执行检查。然后决定是否需要报告问题，还是回复 HEARTBEAT_OK。\n\n让我先读取状态文件，然后执行健康检查脚本。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019cf57f49f1612bffb7458578518678","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/workspace/projects/storage/hooks/heartbeat-state.json"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019cf57f4b929c46a72f87e07a87355e","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"/workspace/projects/workspace/scripts/health-check.sh"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":9272,"output":382,"cacheRead":29440,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39094,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773645280728}}
